{"query":"mutation RegisterUser(
  $firstName: String,
  $lastName: String,
  $email: String,
  $password: String,
  $password2: String,
  $bio1: String,
  $bio2: String,
  $bio3: String,
  $tagline: String,
  $avatar: String,
  $linkedInURL: String,
  $twitterURL: String,
  $facebookURL: String
) {
  registerUser(
    firstName: $firstName,
  	lastName: $lastName,
  	email: $email,
  	password: $password,
    password2: $password2,
  	bio1: $bio1
    bio2: $bio2
    bio3: $bio3
    tagline: $tagline
    avatar: $avatar
    linkedInURL: $linkedInURL
    twitterURL: $twitterURL
    facebookURL: $facebookURL
  ){
    firstName
    lastName
    email
    password
    bio1
    bio2
    bio3    
    tagline
    avatar
    linkedInURL
    twitterURL
    facebookURL
    verificationToken
  }
}

mutation VerifyUser($token: String!) {
  verifyUser(token: $token) {
    id
    verificationToken
    verified
  }
}","variables":{"firstName":"Test1","lastName":"McTesterson","email":"test21@test.com","password":"password","password2":"password","bio1":"Lorem ipsum","bio2":"Lorem ipsum","bio3":"Lorem ipsum","tagline":"Some tagline goes here","avatar":"http://fillmurray.com/200/200","linkedInURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","twitterURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","facebookURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","token":"2361674fb02b165072f956acb68fbbaf88a64dcd"},"operationName":"VerifyUser"}

mutation UpdateUser(
  $id: ID!,
  $firstName: String,
  $lastName: String,
  $email: String,
  $password: String,
  $password2: String,
  $bio1: String,
  $bio2: String,
  $bio3: String,
  $tagline: String,
  $avatar: String,
  $linkedInURL: String,
  $twitterURL: String,
  $facebookURL: String
) {
  updateUser(
    id: $id,
    firstName: $firstName,
  	lastName: $lastName,
  	email: $email,
  	password: $password,
    password2: $password2,
  	bio1: $bio1
    bio2: $bio2
    bio3: $bio3
    tagline: $tagline
    avatar: $avatar
    linkedInURL: $linkedInURL
    twitterURL: $twitterURL
    facebookURL: $facebookURL
  ){
    id
    firstName
    lastName
    email
    password
    bio1
    bio2
    bio3    
    tagline
    avatar
    linkedInURL
    twitterURL
    facebookURL
  }
}

mutation DeleteUserRequest {
  deleteUserRequest
}

mutation DeleteUser($id: ID!, $verificationToken: String!) {
  deleteUser(id: $id, verificationToken: $verificationToken)
}

{"query":"query GetProject($id: ID!) {
  project(id:$id){
    id
  }
}

query allProject {
  allProjects {
    id
    title
    tagline
    user
    author {
      id
    }
    images
  }
}

mutation AddProject(
  $user: ID!
  $title: String!,
  $tagline: String!,
  $about: String,
  $linkedInURL: String,
  $twitterURL: String,
  $facebookURL: String,
  $images: [String]
) {
  addProject(
    title: $title,
  	tagline: $tagline,
    about: $about,
  	user: $user
    linkedInURL: $linkedInURL
    twitterURL: $twitterURL
    facebookURL: $facebookURL
    images: $images
  ){
    id
    user
    title
    tagline
    about
    linkedInURL
    twitterURL
    facebookURL
    images
  }
}

mutation UpdateProject(
  $id: ID!
  $user: ID!
  $title: String!
  $tagline: String!
  $about: String
  $linkedInURL: String
  $twitterURL: String
  $facebookURL: String
  $images: [String]
) {
  updateProject(
    id: $id
    user: $user
    title: $title
  	tagline: $tagline
    about: $about
    linkedInURL: $linkedInURL
    twitterURL: $twitterURL
    facebookURL: $facebookURL
    images: $images
  ){
    id
    user
    title
    tagline
    about
    linkedInURL
    twitterURL
    facebookURL
    images
  }
}

mutation DeleteProject($id: ID!) {
  deleteProject(id: $id)
}","variables":{"id":"5cb3186f9f4b24c07495a61f","title":"Updated Test Blog title","tagline":"Some tagline for the blog","about":"Lorem ipsum","user":"5cb31627670bc9d5065248a5","linkedInURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","twitterURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","facebookURL":"https://www.linkedin.com/me","images":["http://www.fillmurray.com/200/200","http://www.fillmurray.com/200/200","http://www.fillmurray.com/200/200","http://www.fillmurray.com/200/200"]},"operationName":"allProject"}
